        "subject": "Regarding Your Inquiry",
        "emailType": "text",
        "message": "=Hi {{ $('On form submission').item.json['What is your name?'] }},\n\nThank you for reaching out to AI Shakthi.\n\nWe have reviewed your inquiry. At this time, we may not be the best fit for your specific requirement, as our expertise is focused on AI agents, workflow automation, software development, and system integrations.\n\nBased on our review, your current requirement falls outside our core service offerings.\n\nWe appreciate your interest in AI Shakthi and wish you success in finding the right partner for your needs.\n\nRegards,\n\nSandhiya T S\nCEO\nAI Shakthi",
        "options": {}
      },
